Class TuiCommand

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am01.client.tui.commands.TuiCommand
Direct Known Subclasses:
AuthenticateCommand, ChangeFocusedPlayerCommand, ConnectCommand, CreateGameCommand, DrawCardCommand, ExitFinishedGameCommand, JoinCommand, PlaceCardCommand, QuitCommand, ResumeGameCommand, SelectColorCommand, SelectObjectiveCommand, SelectStartingCardSideCommand, SendMessageCommand, SetBoardVisibilityCommand, SetChatVisibilityCommand, SetManualVisibilityCommand, SetObjectivesVisibilityCommand, SetVisibleCardSideCommand, StartGameCommand
public abstract class TuiCommand extends Object
This class represents a generic Tui command. Command is a sequence of instructions that can be executed by the players. Players use commands to interact with the application.
